{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_28","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated job failed to complete cleanly for `org.mongodb:bson:4.11.1`. Preserved work is available on this branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2717-library-new-request-org.mongodb-bson-4.11.1-e1ce75b5\n\nThe most likely failing stage is metadata collection during `generateMetadata`, not the generated library tests themselves. In `logs/org.mongodb:bson:4.11.1/native-test-verify/cycle-0-generateMetadata-2026-05-04T19-23-48-687202Z.log`, `:generateMetadata` fails because the nested `:test` task cannot load `native-image-agent` (`libnative-image-agent.so: cannot open shared object file`). The same failure signature also appears in `logs/org.mongodb:bson:4.11.1/native-test-verify/cycle-0-generateMetadata-2026-05-04T19-15-07-203102Z.log`. By contrast, the later verification runs in `logs/org.mongodb:bson:4.11.1/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-04T19-34-07-340835Z.log` and `logs/org.mongodb:bson:4.11.1/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-04T19-35-13-207999Z.log` end with `BUILD SUCCESSFUL`, and `stats/org.mongodb/bson/4.11.1/stats.json` / `stats/org.mongodb/bson/4.11.1/execution-metrics.json` report `25/25` dynamic-access coverage (100.00%). The generated tests on the preserved branch also appear library-specific rather than scaffold placeholders. The debugging notes in `logs/org.mongodb:bson:4.11.1/metadata-fix/codex.log` point to inherited Gradle JVM selection (`org.gradle.java.home`) as the likely reason the nested agent run missed the GraalVM `native-image-agent`.\n\nPlease inspect:\n- `logs/org.mongodb:bson:4.11.1/native-test-verify/cycle-0-generateMetadata-2026-05-04T19-23-48-687202Z.log`\n- `logs/org.mongodb:bson:4.11.1/native-test-verify/cycle-0-generateMetadata-2026-05-04T19-15-07-203102Z.log`\n- `logs/org.mongodb:bson:4.11.1/metadata-fix/codex.log`\n- `logs/org.mongodb:bson:4.11.1/g